<taxonomicNameLabel box="[680,762,1223,1246]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1656" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(A) Epandrium, cerci and surstylus in caudal view. (B) Same in lateral view. (C) Hypandrium, pre- and postgonite and phallus in lateral view. (D) Same in dorsal view. (E) Male fifth sternite in ventral view. Scales: 0.1 mm for (Aâ€“D), 0.25 mm for (E).
</paragraph>
</caption>
