<subSubSection pageId="9" pageNumber="1657" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="9.[160,1155,430,560]" box="[160,262,430,456]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1657">
<heading bold="true" box="[160,262,430,456]" fontSize="11" level="4" pageId="9" pageNumber="1657" reason="0">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[160,262,430,456]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="1657">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[160,1155,430,560]" pageId="9" pageNumber="1657">
This species is characterized by a narrow frons, only three postsutural dorsocentral setae, a pale brownish tinged wing and brown lower calypter. It is known only from the northeastern part of Yunnan Province, 
<collectingCountry box="[605,672,536,560]" name="China" pageId="9" pageNumber="1657">China</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
